descriptionHtml:
Hey, this is my first time uploading a file so, please be nice. Since I first got Skyrim on launch, I became one of those people who spent hours with the game sliders; at first I was using a Female Nord but thankfully for the creator of  \"The Ashen Race - HD\" http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/8583//? (Seren4XX and RadioRagae)  I tinkered with the sliders for a couple days more; this is what I created, a Asian Female. I tried to make her look as realistic and believable as possible like a girl could pass on the sidewalk and not a anime character. 


I found this tool on the Nexus to copy my character on to a new clean save. http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/15307/?tab=1&navtag=%2Fajax%2Fmoddescription%2F%3Fid%3D15307%26preview%3D&pUp=1 (nycz)


If your someone like me who has played over 700 Hours in skyrim (Beleve it or not, I actually have a life :P  ) you don\'t want to start a new character, use this tool and load the save file I\'ve provided and your own save you wish to use. MAKE SURE YOU CREATE A BACKUP!!!!!!!. You will need Apachii Hair or Apachii Hair Females http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/10168//? (apachii)  also, The Eyes of beauty (LogRaam) http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/13722//?

Thank You Seren4XX and RadioRagae for The Ashen Race - HD 
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/8583//?
